WEBVTT

00:01.484 --> 00:03.020
Previously on "Rescue Me"...

00:03.088 --> 00:05.014
You want to memorialize somebody?

00:05.134 --> 00:07.890
You do it by talking
about their deeds.

00:07.959 --> 00:10.933
Have to remember the firefighters on
the morning of 9/11,

00:11.053 --> 00:13.077
they memorialized themselves

00:13.567 --> 00:16.532
by writing notes to their loved
ones and leaving in the lockers.

00:16.601 --> 00:19.468
I wrote some letters.
I kind of took what

00:19.537 --> 00:20.972
Feinberg was saying
the other day to heart.

00:21.092 --> 00:22.437
You want me to give these,
like, a proofread?

00:22.506 --> 00:23.511
Do not read them.

00:23.631 --> 00:25.636
I won't. I will not read them.

00:29.576 --> 00:32.055
I had a white or a blue shirt on
with stripes on my arm,

00:32.174 --> 00:34.933
I bet you I could do a better job at keeping
some loose cannon prick in line!

00:35.053 --> 00:36.520
Oh, you know what, I would love
to give you

00:36.589 --> 00:38.623
the keys to the kingdom for a couple days.
Chief?

00:38.691 --> 00:40.258
- 5 days.
- Oh ho ho!

00:40.508 --> 00:42.760
Quiet. You're acting
lieutenant for 5 days, however

00:42.880 --> 00:45.537
all decisions must run through me.
You understand?

00:45.606 --> 00:46.905
Cool.

00:46.974 --> 00:48.105
What the hell are you doing?

00:48.225 --> 00:49.942
That's mine!

00:50.062 --> 00:53.446
What is wrong with you?

00:53.515 --> 00:55.964
Oh, my God.

00:57.685 --> 00:59.528
What are you doing here?

00:59.648 --> 01:03.021
I never let you read that letter
because it is the truly only

01:03.090 --> 01:06.455
secret thing that Jimmy and I
will ever have ever again.

01:07.626 --> 01:09.983
Get out.

01:12.493 --> 01:14.768
Ok.

