02:02.253 --> 02:03.340
Look at the floor.

02:03.460 --> 02:07.931
Huh? You could eat right off of it.
Not that I'm encouraging you to eat.

02:08.252 --> 02:12.440
You know, now that
morale is at an all-time low,

02:12.509 --> 02:15.644
