the streets, get into the shed.

04:12.330 --> 04:13.196
Yeah.

04:13.265 --> 04:14.465
Ride along.

04:14.534 --> 04:16.586
And you owe me 35
cents for that cigar.

04:19.873 --> 04:20.973
You better get used to it.

04:21.041 --> 04:22.660
You're a boss now.

04:24.011 --> 04:26.645
Yeah, all right.

04:26.714 --> 04:28.012
Hey.

04:29.350 --> 04:31.017
Oh, no, Tom. What is this?

04:31.085 --> 04:32.732
Another love letter?
I don't want it.

04:32.852 --> 04:37.413
Listen. I apologize for baiting you

04:38.239 --> 04:41.677
