and everything, but

04:43.545 --> 04:46.492
listen, you were right, ok,
what you said that day.

04:46.612 --> 04:47.748
I went down to ground zero.

04:47.868 --> 04:52.774
I thought about driving my
truck into the hole, but...

04:54.076 --> 04:56.076
Then I thought about what you
said, and you know what,

04:56.196 --> 05:00.013
I don't want to be number 344, you know?

05:00.082 --> 05:01.982
I'm over that shit, all of it.

05:02.050 --> 05:03.483
The survivor's guilt.

05:03.552 --> 05:08.943
You know, I'm living now in the here and now.
I got a whole new set of priorities.

05:09.768 --> 05:14.299
So you know, this letter--I poured,

05:14.666 --> 05:18.156
you know...
I poured a lot of my...

05:18.539 --> 05:23.950
You know, my innermost... stuff.

05:24.808 --> 05:29.121
That stuff are called feelings.

05:29.565 --> 05:32.189
And you know what, Tom, I'm sorry that
I betrayed your trust

05:32.309 --> 05:33.811
and that I opened the first letter.

05:34.178 --> 05:36.268
It's not very often one
gets a glimpse inside

05:36.388 --> 05:39.707
the secret inner sensitive
life of Tommy Gavin.

05:40.319 --> 05:41.993
Well, this is it.

05:42.061 --> 05:43.431
This is it. This is the real one.

05:43.551 --> 05:44.696
Yeah, and you know the deal.

05:44.765 --> 05:46.951
- I know the deal.
- Ok.

05:47.257 --> 05:49.700
All right? Done. Away.

05:49.769 --> 05:51.165
My word of honor.

05:52.171 --> 05:54.638
We both know your
word is worth shit.

05:54.707 --> 05:57.229
Well, kind of like your feelings,
so I figure we're both equal.

05:57.349 --> 05:59.715
- So there. We're square.
- We're square.

05:59.835 --> 06:02.512
All right. Let me grab a coffee.

06:03.148 --> 06:06.649
You gonna go get changed,
like ride-along Rivera said?

06:06.718 --> 06:08.184
No. I never listen to you.

06:08.253 --> 06:10.319
Why would I listen to that asshole?
You want a coffee?

06:10.388 --> 06:11.387
No, I'm good.

06:11.456 --> 06:12.455
All right.

06:12.524 --> 06:14.019
- See you later.
- Yeah.

06:24.169 --> 06:25.902
