07:39.215 --> 07:43.271
What are you guys doing?
Finalizing the seating chart?

07:52.680 --> 07:55.017
I can't believe I'm
gonna say this.

07:55.626 --> 07:58.860
All the times I wished that
everybody in this house would

07:58.929 --> 08:03.932
just shut their yaps and give
me some peace and some quiet,

08:04.001 --> 08:07.336
somebody please say something.

08:07.456 --> 08:10.906
I want you to go to at least one
meeting a day from now

08:10.975 --> 08:13.951
until the wedding. Ok? And I want you
to promise you will not visit

08:14.071 --> 08:16.778
ground zero again.
And when we tell you what the deal is

08:16.847 --> 08:19.062
with the wedding, you
will not freak out.

08:19.182 --> 08:25.319
- Why am I gonna freak--
- Ah, ah! We discussed this. Yap, no. Zip.

08:25.387 --> 08:29.086
This is my day, ok?
The most important day in my life so far,

08:29.206 --> 08:33.493
so please no yelling, no drinking, ok?
