08:33.562 --> 08:36.330
Why would I make a joke about Sean's--
Dad! No finger-pointing,

08:36.399 --> 08:40.168
no fist-punching, and I forgot.

08:40.236 --> 08:43.471
Uncle Teddy's walking
me down the aisle now.

08:43.539 --> 08:44.869
What?

08:44.989 --> 08:47.409
- Now, don't blow a gasket.
- I'm not blowing a gasket!

08:47.478 --> 08:49.845
- I'm asking--
- Looks like you're already blowing one!

08:49.914 --> 08:53.283
Hey, hey, hey! See, this is why
I'm doing it instead of you.

08:53.351 --> 08:56.519
She'll be walking down the
aisle in her $10,000 dress.

08:56.588 --> 08:59.322
But--but--but--but--but ah ah.
I thought it was 8 grand,

08:59.391 --> 09:01.524
not--what's 10 grand? What's--
The one I fell in love with

09:01.592 --> 09:03.025
was a little bit more expensive.

09:03.093 --> 09:04.894
Let me get this straight.
10 grand now for the dress?

09:04.962 --> 09:06.929
Is this the final price?
There's no more. This is it, right?

09:06.997 --> 09:10.065
10 grand. 10 grand, and I can't drink.
Why don't you just

09:10.134 --> 09:11.700
shoot me in the head while
we're at it, ok?

09:11.769 --> 09:12.968
See? He wants to drink!

09:13.037 --> 09:14.803
You're not in control
of your sobriety.

09:14.872 --> 09:16.592
You know what I really want to do
is punch you in the face right now.

09:16.712 --> 09:18.392
Oh, save that for the
wedding--big, big finish.

09:18.512 --> 09:20.018
- Oh, that's funny.
- Come on, girls. Get the baby.

09:20.138 --> 09:24.179
Let's go. Janet, I really think we ought
to think about going with plan "B".

09:24.247 --> 09:25.013
What's plan "B"?

09:25.081 --> 09:27.749
Come on. Oh, you'll find out.
Come on, girls.

09:27.817 --> 09:29.417
Do you guys have enough diapers?

09:29.485 --> 09:33.120
You'll be the one needing the
diapers with all the shit in here!

09:33.188 --> 09:34.854
He's so funny.

09:34.923 --> 09:37.924
What's he talking about--plan "B"?

09:37.992 --> 09:41.160
Plan "B" is you don't
go to the wedding.

09:42.301 --> 09:45.364
You gotta be kidding me, right?
That I don't go to the wedding at all?

09:45.433 --> 09:47.166
Tommy, it is a celebration.

09:47.234 --> 09:49.034
There will be alcohol everywhere.

09:49.103 --> 09:52.437
Ok, honey, I have not had a
drink in I don't know how long.

09:52.506 --> 09:54.774
When is the last time you
went to a meeting, huh?

09:54.843 --> 09:57.080
- I don't know. I've been so busy--
- Name the meeting. Name the date.

09:57.200 --> 09:58.902
I don't know. It's like 5 weeks
ago or something like that.

09:59.022 --> 10:00.509
No. 3 1/2.

10:00.629 --> 10:02.501
- Ok, 3 1/2. Even better.
- Months.

10:02.621 --> 10:05.644
Oh. Really?

10:05.764 --> 10:08.338
Look, Tommy, the thing that
you did with Sheila--

10:08.458 --> 10:11.552
Ok, even though you didn't drink
a drop, it is a sign.

10:11.858 --> 10:15.757
You are not ready for this. You are not in
a sane state of mind.

10:16.632 --> 10:18.999
So Uncle Teddy is walking her
down that aisle because

10:19.068 --> 10:22.256
the odds are, even with all the alcohol
flowing freely,

10:22.376 --> 10:24.538
we can count on him
to walk a straight line.

10:25.742 --> 10:26.741
Now, did you talk to Mickey?

10:26.810 --> 10:29.059
- No, I haven't--
- Of course not,

10:29.179 --> 10:30.460
because how could you talk to him

10:30.580 --> 10:32.480
when your head is so far up
your own goddamn ass?

10:32.549 --> 10:35.517
Honey, my head is not my ass, ok?

10:35.586 --> 10:37.653
Ok, I want Mickey performing
that ceremony,

10:37.773 --> 10:40.756
and I want you off that rig
and into a safe job.

10:40.876 --> 10:42.739
Yes, somewhere out of harm's way.

10:42.859 --> 10:45.547
Honey...
no, Tommy, this is not a negotiation.

10:45.667 --> 10:49.597
Ok, you want to be a real father to this baby
and not some sperm donor named dad,

10:49.666 --> 10:52.934
then you will get off that
rig and into somewhere safe.

10:53.003 --> 10:57.739
We've talked about this before.
We've tried it before, 9 million discussions.

10:57.808 --> 11:01.976
I--I don't have time to
go to these meetings now.

11:02.045 --> 11:05.414
Get to a goddamn meeting every
goddamn day

11:05.781 --> 11:10.644
and bring me proof! Ok, and do not--and I
repeat--do not

11:10.764 --> 11:12.254
show up at that rehearsal dinner drunk.

11:12.323 --> 11:16.191
I'm not...gonna.

11:16.260 --> 11:21.023
I'll be there. I'll be there,
and I will be sober as a judge.

11:21.451 --> 11:24.167
Ok, good, because that will go
a long way to showing Colleen

11:24.236 --> 11:28.172
that maybe you are capable of
walking her down that aisle.

11:28.241 --> 11:32.279
I'm... capable.

11:32.712 --> 11:34.578
I will be there.

11:34.647 --> 11:35.813
Sober.

11:35.882 --> 11:36.747
As a judge.

11:36.816 --> 11:38.845
Done deal.

11:42.321 --> 11:43.487
You got it.

11:49.927 --> 11:55.131
So, serenity, patience.

11:55.199 --> 11:57.133
Easy does it.

11:57.202 --> 11:59.002
Keeping calm.

11:59.071 --> 12:01.405
I wasn't always the laid-back,
easy-going guy you see before

12:01.474 --> 12:05.375
you here today. There was a time
when the easy-going,

12:05.444 --> 12:07.744
steady guy you see before you
here--

12:07.813 --> 12:10.214
Put whiskey in his orange
juice every morning.

12:10.282 --> 12:13.551
There was a time--
Yeah, Tom.

12:13.619 --> 12:15.599
Sorry. I didn't mean to interrupt,
but

12:15.719 --> 12:19.824
a little bit of a rush. I'm late for work
and got all the wedding

12:19.893 --> 12:21.993
crap going on, as you know.
