12:22.062 --> 12:23.061
to the firehouse, blah, blah, blah.

12:23.129 --> 12:28.333
Can I talk to you--sorry--just
one second privately?

12:28.401 --> 12:32.537
Tom, I'm not going to the wedding.

12:32.606 --> 12:35.244
I really need to kind of
go to the wedding, Mick.

12:36.543 --> 12:39.076
I'm sorry, everybody.
This is my cousin Tommy.

12:39.145 --> 12:40.945
- Hey, Tommy.
- Hi, Tommy.

12:41.014 --> 12:41.813
Hey, everybody. Hey.

12:41.882 --> 12:44.983
He's also a raging--uh, sorry.
He's also in recovery.

12:45.051 --> 12:50.255
Yeah, well, I mean, I wasn't
as bad as him, but whatever.

12:50.324 --> 12:52.123
Oh, is that right?

12:52.192 --> 12:55.768
Well, I wasn't.
I mean, I didn't

12:56.597 --> 12:59.365
put whiskey in my orange juice.
Listen,

12:59.641 --> 13:02.134
just tell me that you're gonna come to the
wedding, and this is all set.

13:02.254 --> 13:03.669
I just really need you
to come to the wedding.

13:03.738 --> 13:04.370
Go to hell.

13:04.439 --> 13:05.138
Hey! Hey!

13:05.206 --> 13:05.938
Go to hell!

13:06.007 --> 13:06.906
Go to hell! Get out!

13:06.975 --> 13:09.208
And you can take that goddamn
wedding and stick it

13:09.277 --> 13:11.541
where the sun don't shine.
She don't apologize to me.

13:11.661 --> 13:14.247
She and I never set foot in the same room
again as long as I live

13:14.316 --> 13:16.026
on this planet!
And you can tell her another thing.

13:16.146 --> 13:21.188
I don't care how hot her ass is, I am never,
ever sleeping with her again!

13:21.257 --> 13:24.425
All right, all right, I get it.
I get it. If you

13:24.494 --> 13:27.996
could just sign this.
It's a little note telling Janet

13:28.064 --> 13:30.365
that I definitely came to the meeting and
I was here for the whole--

13:30.433 --> 13:31.866
- All right, all right.
- Get out!

13:31.935 --> 13:33.301
- I'm going!
- Go!

13:33.370 --> 13:39.307
- Sorry, everybody. Didn't mean to...
- Let me go.

14:09.305 --> 14:13.934
"Dear Lou, you have been more of a brother
to me than even my own blood brother.

14:14.485 --> 14:16.614
The bond between us
goes deeper than the bond

14:16.734 --> 14:20.043
we felt as members of the
firefighting brotherhood.

14:21.051 --> 14:24.752
