started 10 minutes ago. You're late.

15:35.064 --> 15:36.763
Yeah, well, I had a little
family emergency, ok?

15:36.832 --> 15:37.831
Yeah, well, what's new?

15:37.900 --> 15:40.306
Next time, leave it at home.
We got work to do around here, ok?

15:40.426 --> 15:42.669
You know, you're acting
like a real douchebag.

15:42.738 --> 15:44.461
Yeah? Well, it takes one to know one.

15:44.581 --> 15:46.244
So after you're done with your little
milk-and-cookie break,

15:46.364 --> 15:47.851
Opie, I expect you to hop in uni.

15:50.946 --> 15:53.848
Hoo hoo hoo hoo hoo.

15:56.819 --> 15:59.420
Hey. I swear to God.
