All I want is power bars.

16:04.594 --> 16:08.576
Everything's labeled.
What-- crackers...dirty bowls.

16:10.321 --> 16:12.567
Aw, thanks, man.

16:12.636 --> 16:13.868
And it's not just here.

16:13.937 --> 16:16.904
